 <title>AT&amp;T Hackathon a Showcase for AllJoyn’s Role in the Internet of Everything</title>
 <link>https://identity.allseenalliance.org/news/blogs/2014/09/att-hackathon-showcase-alljoyn-s-role-internet-everything</link>
 <description>
		&lt;span class=&quot;a2a_kit a2a_target addtoany_list&quot; id=&quot;da2a_1&quot;&gt;
			&lt;a class=&quot;a2a_button_facebook&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
